50
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,270
Does Chen Pingping have anything for me?

51
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:02,750
Someone wants to kill the Head.

52
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:03,880
In the world,

53
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:04,960
