is protecting the Head.

62
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,630
What do you mean?

63
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,240
Zhuang Mohan has arrived in the capital city.

64
00:03:21,390 --> 00:03:22,110
How is Zhuang Mohan

65
00:03:22,110 --> 00:03:23,080
relevant to this?

66
00:03:23,830 --> 00:03:25,080
Zhuang Mohan's arrival

67
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,750
leads to the change.

68
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:28,720
Everyone in the Investigator's Office knows that

69
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:29,750
the only way to restart the war

70
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,880
is to assassinate Zhuang Mohan.

71
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:36,270
But the Head has sent the First Division

72
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,800
to protect Zhuang Mohan.

73
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,550
Right.

74
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:41,440
Zhu Ge from the First Division

75
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,600
has led all his men out.

76
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:45,000
Fei Jie from the Third Division is not in the capital city.

77
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,240
Martial arts masters from other divisions

78
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,880
have been sent out by me respectively.

79
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,600
Today, all the officials inside

80
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,000
the Investigator's Office are on our side.

81
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:54,440
Even so, we don't have enough men

82
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,190
to kill Zhuang Mohan.

83
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,160
Zhuang Mohan is just a cover.

84
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,240
The person we're really going to kill

85
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,160
is Chen Pingping.

86
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:27,640
You're here.

87
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,160
We have no way out.

88
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:36,950
Let's go to the dungeon.

89
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:41,160
You all know that

90
00:04:41,550 --> 00:04:42,790
Chen Pingping is the person

91
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:43,640
preventing us from restarting the war

92
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,600
in the Investigator's Office.

93
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,760
If he dies,

94
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,230
the Investigator's Office will be controlled

95
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,880
by loyal people like us.

96
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,550
By then, it will be very easy

97
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,720
to motivate His Majesty

98
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,230
to destroy Beiqi.

99
00:04:56,550 --> 00:04:57,390
He's also a man.

100
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,480
I've exhausted my abilities

101
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:00,550
to create a favorable situation for us.

102
00:05:01,110 --> 00:05:02,920
If we don't kill him today, we won't have a second chance.

103
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:05,350
Kill Chen Pingping! Kill Chen Pingping!

104
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:07,950
Kill Chen Pingping!

105
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,230
Once Chen Pingping is killed,

106
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,070
the Investigator's Office

107
00:05:11,350 --> 00:05:12,920
will be controlled by us.

108
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,790
What's done is done.

109
00:05:16,550 --> 00:05:17,640
There's no way back.

110
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:19,270
Let's do it!

111
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:25,440
Kill Chen Pingping! Kill Chen Pingping!

112
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,600
Kill Chen Pingping!

113
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:35,600
Mr. Fan?

114
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:38,510
Miss Lili, let's talk later.

115
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:39,320
We're being hunted.

116
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:41,000
Hunted?

117
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,950
Press that.

118
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:01,720
It leads to

119
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,110
the deepest part of the dungeon,

120
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,200
where the most vicious villains

121
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,200
are locked up inside.

122
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,830
Let's get inside first.

123
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:21,160
Are we safe here?

124
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,350
Not really.

125
00:06:22,350 --> 00:06:24,110
Many people know this path.

126
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:25,200
They usually deliver water

127
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,510
and food to the prisoners.

128
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,110
Sometimes,

129
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:28,350
they have to pull out the bodies.

130
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,880
Then what's the point of hiding here?

131
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,320
It's narrow inside. Maybe we can resist them for a while.

132
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:34,390
Then we'll have to die sooner or later.

133
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:36,760
It's a dead end.

134
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:41,670
This is terrible!

135
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,230
I can't die.

136
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,160
I haven't told my wife yet.

137
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,440
If I die without her permission,

138
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,720
she will definitely be angry.

139
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,550
We're in great danger,

140
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:55,200
yet you're afraid your wife might be angry.

141
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,200
Life or death, it doesn't matter.

142
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:59,350
What really matters is
whether I've gained permission from my wife or not.

143
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,000
You don't understand.

144
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,760
What will happen to Si Lili outside?

145
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,830
They want to kill me.

146
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:11,760
They won't leave anyone alive.

147
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:14,790
Give me the key to her cell.

148
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,270
You can't even protect yourself. Why care about others?

149
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,110
The key!

150
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,200
Wait a minute.

151
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,200
He's a good lad.

152
00:07:39,230 --> 00:07:40,070
What's the sound?

153
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:42,510
What's the sound?

154
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,950
Is there an internal strife in the Investigator's Office?

155
00:07:59,230 --> 00:08:00,270
Why do you save me?

156
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,270
Hurry up!

157
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,350
They could rush in any minute.

158
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:08,830
Kill Chen Pingping! Kill Chen Pingping!

159
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:11,390
Kill Chen Pingping!

160
00:08:12,550 --> 00:08:15,670
Kill him!

161
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:29,320
What's the point of

162
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,040
bringing me here?

163
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,320
I still have to die.

164
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,640
I've promised you to protect you.

165
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,790
Even if you have to die,

166
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,110
you must die after me.

167
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,350
Go inside.

168
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,030
Your Excellency.

169
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,110
What's this?

170
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:48,400
I've told you about

171
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:49,640
the prisoners locked up here.

172
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:51,470
The most vicious villains?

173
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,640
Right.

174
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,640
One of them is still alive.

175
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,400
So many chains are used to lock up only one person?

176
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,080
Yes, only one.

177
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:11,470
Will your life be saved after looking at him?

178
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,590
This way.

179
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,520
He's not here.

180
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:18,440
Hurry up and find Chen Pingping!

181
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:25,840
He's not here.

182
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,200
No, He's not here. He's not here.

183
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,640
He's not here.

184
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,520
Where is he?

185
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,440
Go inside and find him!

186
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:34,520
He's not here.

187
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,440
Wait a moment!

188
00:09:58,030 --> 00:09:59,000
I'm going to die.

189
00:09:59,000 --> 00:09:59,960
Can I at least satisfy

190
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,590
my curiosity?

191
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,230
Is he really dangerous?

192
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,320
Indeed!

193
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:10,910
His name is Xiao En.

194
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:15,840
I was paralyzed because of him.

195
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,280
Chen Pingping is inside.

196
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:20,840
He has no way to go.

197
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:23,470
-Kill him! -Come on!

198
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:25,840
Kill him!

199
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,710
-Kill him! -Kill Chen Pingping!

200
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,520
They've opened the door

201
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,880
to the secret path.

202
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:35,200
-Kill Chen Pingping! -Kill Chen Pingping!

203
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:41,550
Catch him!

204
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:44,320
Si Lili.

205
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:46,760
What?

206
00:10:47,710 --> 00:10:48,520
Beiqi is defeated.

207
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,080
Why do you tell me that?

208
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:53,670
I'm nervous. I have to say something.

209
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,200
Actually there's another way

210
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,030
to save our lives.

211
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:07,000
They only want to kill Chen Pingping.

212
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,910
Do you believe they will

213
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:12,710
let us go?

214
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:14,400
We can kill him first.

215
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:17,110
Then we can trade his head for our lives.

216
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,440
This is the only way to save our lives.

217
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:31,470
Wang Qinian.

218
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:32,470
Your Excellency.

219
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:34,080
Let's take the risk.

220
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:35,910
OK.

221
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:38,520
What are you doing?

222
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:39,320
Just wait.

223
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,320
It's Shadow! He's alone!

224
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,150
Kill him!

225
00:11:46,350 --> 00:11:47,840
-He's alone! -Kill him!

226
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,880
Kill him!

227
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,080
All the men outside are martial arts masters.

228
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:52,280
How long can he hold by himself?

229
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,710
The noise of fighting is further and further away from us.

230
00:12:19,590 --> 00:12:20,470
He has killed a way out?

231
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:22,760
Are those opponents

232
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,550
too weak?

233
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,840
They are all martial arts masters above the Seventh Dan.

234
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:30,110
It's really not my idea.

235
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:36,200
What did you just say?

236
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:41,080
Shadow wants to test you.

237
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:42,840
It's not my idea.

238
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:43,880
What?

239
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,840
Test me?

240
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:48,150
Are those men outside acting?

241
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:50,200
They do want to kill me.

242
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,790
Are there other martial arts masters

243
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,590
ambushing in the dark?

244
00:12:52,590 --> 00:12:53,590
There aren't any reinforcements.

245
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,280
Then why do you say it's a test?

246
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:58,200
Shadow alone can resist one thousand cavalrymen.

247
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,840
I don't know.

248
00:13:01,350 --> 00:13:02,320
I've never seen Master Shadow

249
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,320
in a fight.

250
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,670
Si Lili,

251
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:10,150
just now when Shadow left

252
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:10,710
and the other two

253
00:13:10,710 --> 00:13:11,960
were not by my side,

254
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:14,230
I thought you would hold me hostage.

255
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:17,110
That might be your last chance

256
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,520
to escape.

257
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:22,960
I know.

258
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,080
Why did you hesitate?

259
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,910
I dared not.

260
00:13:31,280 --> 00:13:32,080
In Beiqi,

261
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,470
Chen Pingping

262
00:13:35,230 --> 00:13:36,670
is as scary as demons.

263
00:13:42,350 --> 00:13:43,470
Push me out.

264
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:52,640
Chen Pingping,

265
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:57,910
don't die. Wait for me to get out.

266
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:08,030
He's afraid I might be killed by others.

267
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:10,670
He won't get out.

268
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,910
Let's go.

269
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,080
So you knew

270
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,080
they wanted to kill you?

271
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:33,790
Yes.

272
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,520
Yet you just let them.

273
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:38,350
Independent from the Six
Ministries, the Investigator's Office

274
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:39,440
is an important organization with great power.

275
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:40,670
Though I'm the Head,

276
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,520
I can't guard against the world.

277
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,150
There will always be organizations

278
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,910
finding ways to plant agents

279
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,910
who are good at hiding themselves.

280
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:49,550
By giving them the chance to kill me,

281
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,880
they would jump out

282
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,520
and be exposed once and for all.

283
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,400
Wang Qinian.

284
00:15:16,710 --> 00:15:18,150
Use yourself as bait.

285
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,150
Smart as they are,

286
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:22,400
they wouldn't be tricked

287
00:15:22,710 --> 00:15:23,710
without seeing me.

