417
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:23,800
To me,

418
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:25,560
Fan Xian is not qualified.

419
00:22:25,560 --> 00:22:26,950
Are you mistaken?

420
00:22:28,470 --> 00:22:30,310
I'm not here to asking for your approval.

421
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,280
